00:36:24.560 --> 00:36:27.330
Because m what
we're trying to do

00:36:27.330 --> 00:36:32.750
is to create justice
for our citizens.

00:36:32.750 --> 00:36:35.530
But to do that, you
have to actually believe

00:36:35.530 --> 00:36:37.930
that your neighbor
is your citizen.

00:36:37.930 --> 00:36:41.730
And in a country like
this, and a city like this,

00:36:41.730 --> 00:36:43.700
that can be a difficult thing.

00:36:43.700 --> 00:36:45.740
So I do believe it's
a bedrock question.

00:36:45.740 --> 00:36:48.940
